tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE lobbyists (
    lobbyist_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    lobbyist_name STRING,
    interaction_date DATE,
    interaction_type STRING,
    lawmaker_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE lobbyists (id INT PRIMARY KEY, name VARCHAR(255), organization VARCHAR(255), contact_info VARCHAR(255));
CREATE TABLE interactions (id INT PRIMARY KEY, lobbyist_id INT, lawmaker_id INT, date DATE, description TEXT);

CREATE TABLE interactions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  lobbyist_id INT,
  lawmaker_id INT,
  date DATE,
  description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE lobbyists (
  lobbyist_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  contact_info VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE lawmakers (
  lawmaker_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  party VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE interactions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  lobbyist_id INT REFERENCES lobbyists(lobbyist_id),
  lawmaker_id INT REFERENCES lawmakers(lawmaker_id),
  interaction_date DATE NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE bills (
  bill_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  title VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE interactions (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  lobbyist_id INT NOT NULL,
  lawmaker_id INT NOT NULL,
  meeting_date DATE NOT NULL,
  purpose TEXT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE meetings (
  id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
  lobbyist_id INT NOT NULL,
  lawmaker_id INT NOT NULL,
  location VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  notes TEXT
);
